tatami.core.agent

Class BaseAgent

  • java.lang.Object
    • GuiAgent
      • tatami.core.agent.BaseAgent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParametrizedAgent
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    VisualizableAgent

    public class BaseAgent
extends GuiAgent
implements ParametrizedAgent
    The base layer of the agent. It handles the interface with Jade, agent parameters, and knowledge.

    It is extended on top of and works directly with Jade's GuiAgent.

    It implements ParametrizedAgent, contains the list of agent's parameters and implements methods for working with parameters.

    Author:
    Andrei Olaru

      • parameters

        private ParametrizedAgent.AgentParameters parameters
        The agent's parameters.

        They can only be accessed by this level of the agent, which serves them to the layers above through specialized functions.

      • knowledgeBase

        private final KnowledgeBase knowledgeBase
        The agent's knowledge base. It cannot be changed (i.e. create a different instance) throughout the agent's lifecycle. It can only be accessed by this level of the agent, which serves knowledge-related requests to the layers above through specialized functions.
